cdata.name: LevelNet Token
cdata.desc: LevelNet is a project that integrated virtually all existing anti-virus technologies into an intuitive application that allows participants to share threat data globally. This allows the entire LevelNet system to become adaptive to new threats. LVL is an ERC20 token based on the Ethereum network. LVL Token holders will be able to use LevelNet services, the LevelNet ecosystem, and all its products, in addition to receiving use of intellectual property rights. It will be possible to exchange tokens for crypto shares in the second phase of the project.
